(107,	'en_us',	'Page',	16,	'content',	'<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif;\">ChalkPro offers a fun service, but please remember: play responsibly!. And committed to supporting responsible gambling behavior, in spreading knowledge in relation to gambling addiction and improve political intervention and treatment of this problem. The Responsible Gaming Policy ChalkPro has as its goal the reduction of the negative aspects of gambling addiction and promote an attitude of responsible gaming. Online gambling may become an addiction, as can happen in any other situation is taken to excess. It can happen to any person lose control of their game. This page contains some useful advice and resources for avoid becoming an addiction. Here you can find help if you ever need it.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Under 18&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">The law prohibits children under 18 years of opening an account or to gamble on sites ChalkPro. The minors who were discovered to play on these sites will lose their winnings and the incident could be reported to the authorities.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Tips for using&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">ChalkPro considers it his duty to make sure that our customers can enjoy wagering on our site, while remaining aware of possible social and economic damage associated with gambling. The game can be a pleasant and exciting time of fun, but must exert self-control, behave accordingly and follow some basic principles.&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Exploits the ability of the free online games. You will get used sound effects and graphics and, in particular learn the rules of the game.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Never bet more than you can afford.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Never play when tired or under the influence of alcohol.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Put a limit on your winnings. Once you\'ve reached it put a little \'aside and play with the remaining money.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Do not get yourself into debt in order to play,&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">controls and limits on the game&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Trebuchet, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">In order to better support our players to allow them to gamble appropriate to their ability, impart appropriate training to our staff on responsible gambling and have implemented the following information and functionality within our site through the live chat you can ask to limit your bets.</span></span></p>'),
(229,	'en_us',	'Page',	30,	'title',	'FAQ & SUPPORT'),
(230,	'en_us',	'Page',	30,	'content',	'<p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Here Are Answers to the Most Asked Questions on yourdomain.com (FAQ)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">How can I use yourdomain.com?</span></strong><br /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong>yourdomain.com</strong>&nbsp;is a sports betting site where you can make predictions on matches and win bets as you get your predictions right. It\'s all about trading on the results of sports matches. There IS ALWAYS money to be won on ALL the outcome of football matches. You don\'t even have to predict the exact score line. Just a home win, draw or away win will do.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">Each match and outcome have their own prices (called odds). You will have relatively small money to be won if you&nbsp;<a id=\"_GPLITA_1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 12px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: gray;\" title=\"Click to Continue &gt; by Browse to Save\" href=\"http://www.1960sportsbook.com/pages/contacts#\">bet on</a>&nbsp;a BIG team to beat a small team but there will be high returns if you back the smaller teams to win or to draw.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">So how do I start using yourdomain.com?</strong><br />You start by registering on the site. Once registered, an email containing an activation link will be sent to your email. upon receipt of the email, click on the link to activate your registered account. Next, fund your account and start betting. It\'s that easy!<br /><br /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">How do I fund my account?</strong><br />When logged in, click on \"<span style=\"color: #808080; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-style: inherit;\">Deposit</span></span>\" and proceed to make payment using any of the payment methods listed. Click on \"Manual\" if you made payment using bank transfer; Enter the amount that you deposited, and your yourdomain.com account will be funded as soon as payment is confirmed. Please note that the bank accounts on the page could be updated from time to time, so always check the page for the bank most convenient for you before making deposits. In the near future, other methods of payment will be rolled out.<br /><br /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">How long does a deposit take before it reflects in my yourdomain.com account?</strong><br />Optimally, this should take not more than an hour. But the maximum time it should take from the time you post your deposit details to when your yourdomain.com account is credited, is 4 hours. Members are advised not to dispose of their deposit slips until they confirm that their accounts have been credited.<br /><br /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">What should I do if my account has not been credited after 24 hours?</strong><br />Use the \"Contact Us\" link at the top of the page when logged in to contact the support desk. Your request/problem will be acted on promptly.<br /><br /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">Can I pay cash at your office?</strong><br />We do not accept cash at any of our offices. All deposits should be made online using debit cards, or into any of our bank accounts or as may be stated in the \"Add Funds\" page.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">What Is The Meaning Of 1, X and 2?</span></strong><br /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">The teams listed first is 1, the second listed is 2 and draw is X.</span></p>\r\n<p><em><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">Let me give an example:</span></em></p>\r\n<p><em><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">1 X 2<br />Barcelona V Man Utd 2.2 &nbsp;3.0 &nbsp;2.2<br />This means the price on Barcelona to win (first team listed first) is 2.2<br />Man Utd to win (second team to be listed) is also 2.2<br />A draw is priced at 3.0<br /></span></em><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><br /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">What Is The Meaning Of MultiBet (Accumulator)?<br /></strong>Accumulator means adding matches for potential higher returns.<br /><em><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">For example: if Man Utd to beat Chelsea is priced at 2.0 and Everton to beat Arsenal is priced at 3.0, you can add (accumulate) the 2 matches. Your potential returns will be 2.0 times 3.0 which is 6</span></em><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">The downside is that once one result goes wrong, your accumulator goes wrong.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">I Can See A Referral Code In My Account. What Does It Mean?</span></strong><br /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">The referral program is what we use to reward our users when they refer people to our website. A user can earn up to 20% of the initial deposit of those he/she referred to our site.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 12px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Can I cancel my bet?</span></strong><br /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 12px;\">No. Once it has been confirmed, you cannot cancel a bet. Please check your bet details carefully before submitting your bet to us.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 8pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">What should I do if I have any problems with my account or transaction issues?</strong><br />Use the \"Contact us\" link at the top of the page when logged in to contact the support desk for prompt response.<br /><br /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">My question is not answered here. What should I do?</strong><br />Please send your inquiries by email to: support<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 12px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: gray; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"mailto:info@1960sportsbook.com\">@yourdomain.com</a>.</span></p>'),
