(136,	'en_us',	'Page',	22,	'content',	'<p>This Regulation shall enter into force on 1 July 2005. This regulation must be known and accepted unconditionally by the customer when opening an account. All bets are gathered by ChalkPro subject to the rules, listed below, which are subject to change by the company, at its sole discretion. These changes will be posted on the site.</p>\r\n<p>- Account opening and management -</p>\r\n<p>The service and opening a betting account ChalkPro is allowed only to adults (18 years). The person who opens an account ChalkPro recognizes and accepts all definitions and conditions set forth in these Regulations are required also to control the news, changes in quotas, permissions, the cancellation of coupons, etc..&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To be able to bet with ChalkPro you must open a deposit account. With the opening of the account codes will be assigned to the customer and / or passwords that are necessary to access the same. The account holder is responsible for the confidentiality of such codes and / or passwords as a result ChalkPro deemed valid bets made by a third party in possession of such information.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Each customer can open only one betting account in your name. ChalkPro reserves the right to close the account at any time and to cancel all transactions of any customer who has opened more than one account in his name different names or if ChalkPro has reason to believe that the opening of these multiple accounts has been made with the purpose to defraud and cheat the company.The user, by opening an account with ChalkPro, implicitly authorizes the processing of personal data in accordance with applicable laws on privacy. The processing of personal data and \'aimed exclusively maintaining the account for the use of services offered by ChalkPro.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The Company reserves the right to close a customer\'s account at any time, without justifying this choice. In this case the customer will be sent their account balan