n style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">Click on any sport you wan to bet on, click on football to have access to leagues available.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">Image 20.png</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">If you want other sports, you can click on the particular sport you want.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">Everything is well arranged for easy navigation.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">A picture they say is worth a thousand words. Let us take a look like you</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">are ready to bet. Lets click on England to see what comes up.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">See the image below</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">.Image 22.png</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">Image 21.png</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">Using the image above as example, let us assume you want to choose</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">Fulham, Tottenham, Man Utd and Chelsea to win. All you have to do is click</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">on the odds one after the other.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">there are always three odds for each matches. the first odd is what you get</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">if the first team win. The second odd is what you get if the teams draw and the</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">last odd is what you get if the away team win.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">In a nutshell, whichever team you want to back to win, just click on the</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">odd. If you think the match will end in a draw, just click on middle odd. It is</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">very easy to do. As you click on your choice, the team selected will be</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">added to your bet slip on the right hand side. See where the arrow the</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">image below is pointing to.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">Image 27.png</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">If you want to stake on just a single match, select the match and finish the</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">bet and then select another one if you want to continue. It is when you</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">want to accumulate that you should select more than one match.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">Anyway, after selecting the matches you want, you can then proceed to</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">bet. Enter the amount you want to bet with in the space provided beside</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&ldquo;stake&rdquo;. Click on Preview under your bet slip.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">Image 29.png</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&nbsp;Click &nbsp;\"Submit Ticket\" to complete your bet.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">Image 30.png</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">&nbsp;I forgot to say that you can accumulate matches from different countries.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">In the example above, if you want to add another bet from another country</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">into your accumulator, simply click on the country on the left hand side.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">Your bet slip will remain intact. After adding it, you can place your bet.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">If you win, your account will be credited within 10 minutes after the</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.909090042114258px;\">matches are played. It\'s that simple.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20