in the list appear the sign and the value assigned to the VV share will be equal to 1.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If a match is postponed for any reason, the official date of Association concerned, and not disputed within 24 hours, the result for the Null and Void bet you believe (share = 1).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Disputes or complaints relating to bets must be made before of the event contested.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The maximum possible payout is 1000 times the mail for all types of bets.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>ChalkPro is free to terminate its relationship with any customer without any justification. In this case, the entitlement will be paid at closing account. The same procedure is followed for wagers still in progress and which will fail.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The press of the future challenge is not received, so a bet will be considered successful only if the same is on Betslip user.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The company ChalkPro, in particular periods or sporting events, reserves the right to give incentives in the form of bonuses to multiple bets the value of which will be defined from time to times</p>\r\n<p>In case of obvious errors in the publication of the shares ChalkPro reserves the right to intervene by changing the odds mistakenly published Void giving the event with odds equal to 1, even at the end of the event. The customer can request cancellation of the bet just before the start of the event. If error in the publication of the start date of an event, all bets placed after the start or during the event will be considered Void with odd = 1.</p>\r\n<p>- FOOTBALL -</p>\r\n<p>The outcome of football betting is always based on the 90 minutes of play more regulatory recovery, do not include any extra time, golden goal or penalties.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>As for the triangular tournament, the outcome of betting and \'time-based regulations of the game (45 minutes), do not include any extra time or penalties.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>H / F: Half time / Full time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This bet takes into account the game and divided into 2 phases. In the first you have to guess how it ends the first time (1, X, 2), in the second you have to guess how it ends the game (1, X 2)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Half time (1st HT) You have to guess the outcome of the first \"1-X-2\" (45 minutes including injury time).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2nd Half Time (2nd HT) is the second time, including minutes of recovery.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Double Chance: in this case the three possible signs 1, X 2, are grouped into 3 groups 1X, 12, and X2, facilitating the task of the player. Of course, the odds will be a consequence mathematics.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Correct Score : you have to guess exactly how a result ends the game.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Over / Under: you have to guess if a game will be more or fewer goals compared to the number ChalkPro gives as a reference.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2nd HALF BETTING&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In this type of bet is taken into account only the second time a football game! The shares will be offered in the interval between the first and second time, then have to predict the outcome regardless the first time between the two opposing teams who win the second time (Including injury time).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Goal / No Goal - Matching with all events (multiple). This means that in a bet selections may appear with signs NG GG or together with other events.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>DD - This sign can be considered valid when both the teams to score, therefore it is independent of the number of goals in the outcome. Ex (1-1, 1-2, 2-2, etc.).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>NG - This sign can be considered valid when at least one of the teams do not marks, so that present only the results are worth \"zero\" for at least one either team or both. Ex (0-0, 1-0, 0-1, 2-0, 0-2, etc.)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>TOTAL GOALS Predict the number of goals scored in a game that will be (This total can be exactly 0 and 1 goal, just 2 goals; exactly 3 goals or 4 goals or more).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Odd / Even&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You have to guess if the sum of the final goal of a meeting of football has outcome Odd (Odd) or Even (Odd). Ex-Real Madrid 2-2 Barcelona, in this case Even winning selection will be (even) as the sum of the final score Real Madrid-Barcelona is 4! If the result is 0-0, the result will be considered Even (Odd). This excludes extra time and penalties.&nbsp;</p>'),
